em]]&nbsp;\u2013 Cologne &nbsp;Hbf&nbsp;\u2013 K\u00f6ln Messe/Deutz&nbsp;\u2013 '''Cologne/Bonn Airport'''&nbsp;\u2013 Troisdorf&nbsp;\u2013 (Hennef&nbsp;\u2013 Herchen&nbsp;\u2013  Au (Sieg))\n| Every 20 minutes\n|}\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Commonscat-inline|Bahnhof K\u00f6ln/Bonn Flughafen|Cologne/Bonn Airport station}}\n\n{{NBS K-F}}\n{{Airport stations in Germany}}\n\n[[Category:Railway stations in Cologne]]\n[[Category:Rhine-Ruhr S-Bahn stations]]\n[[Category:Airport railway stations in Germany]]\n[[Category:S13 (Rhine-Ruhr S-Bahn)]]\n[[Category:Railway stations opened in 2004]]\n[[Category:Railway stations located underground in Germany]]\n", "name_user": "Tobibln", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cologne/Bonn_Airport_station"}
